{"tid":1375231,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"用護陰呀﹗﹗","createTime":"2019-07-28T04:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T04:11:34.000Z","uid":24047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6438939258af0d9dcadd9f1409cb2f6a61c7b487","tid":1375231,"uid":24047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:11:34.000Z","msg":"尤其是男士，full gear之餘，勿忘護陰的重要性﹗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n【光復元朗 | 記者第一身視角中彈片段：擊中下體感暈眩 瞓地被急救治理】<br />\n<br />\n警方與示威者於西邊圍牌坊附近對峙期間，瘋狂掃射胡椒球、海綿彈及橡膠子彈，多次擊中記者。本台有記者兩度被胡椒球擊中下半身，其中一發更直接擊中陰部造成劇痛，再加上催淚煙攻上褲襠，該名記者劇痛至產生暈眩感覺，需由在場示威者進行急救。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/207097505984138/posts/3104164636277396?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F207097505984138%2Fposts%2F3104164636277396%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbpxjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=09ff24d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/207097505984138/posts/3104164636277396?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//"}]}